{"tid":2464080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官媒圖降溫︰壞人混進抵制隊伍","createTime":"2021-03-27T07:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T08:27:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":28,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"dddbc83c372411df7d139bb65bc044e83a956785","tid":2464080,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210327/VLK6CGN6SVBQFMU7WL2DBPXPRU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210327%2FVLK6CGN6SVBQFMU7WL2DBPXPRU%2F&d=jrWVSpMJYTM9%2F%2BTkK0Hr30XxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=c8391163\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210327%2FVLK6CGN6SVBQFMU7WL2DBPXPRU%2F&h=d740128f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210327/VLK6CGN6SVBQFMU7WL2DBPXPRU/</a><br />\n<br />\n官媒圖降溫︰壞人混進抵制隊伍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9sNRmnBvS8s--E0frxnhLZuoPd4=/510x362/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YQIWK76NU5EORFSYHXLNWPF2ME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9sNRmnBvS8s--E0frxnhLZuoPd4%3D%2F510x362%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYQIWK76NU5EORFSYHXLNWPF2ME.jpg&h=503c4a72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有內地女子舉牌要求抵制H＆M。<br />\n<br />\n新疆棉事件，引起內地有民眾義和團式抵制西方服裝品牌。正當外界以為事件將持續蔓延、發酵之際，官媒《環球時報》昨凌晨發表的一篇評論文章，稱「抵制H&amp;M的隊伍裏混進了壞人」，形容有人藉風潮推動「加速主義」，「我反對不了你，就給你下套，鼓譟你走向極端，製造分裂」，呼籲民眾「保持理性」，提防煽動。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：總部在瑞士 響應保護維人法案倡停用疆棉 BCI被官媒指收美國錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n促防「高級黑」搞加速主義<br />\n<br />\n抵制H&amp;M、Nike等國際品牌的行動幾近狂熱，《環時》旗下網站「環球網」昨日凌晨發文圖降溫，一。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n文章其後大篇幅敍述。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：小粉紅轟Hugo Boss「彈出彈入」<br />\n《環球時報》"},{"pid":"56ab5f20e10585a4a537dc85512f3034ea9094dc","tid":2464080,"uid":33408,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-2